    • Method Detail

      • initializeGraph

        public void initializeGraph(java.lang.String filepath)
        This function is used to initialize a complete weighted planar graph based on the TSPLIB instance who's path is passed as parameter . Note that for this graph the distance matrix is filled as follows: distance[i,j] = {0 if i==j , euclideanDistance[i,j] if i=/=j}.
        Specified by:
        initializeGraph in class Graph
        Parameters:
        filepath - Stores the path of the TSPLIB instance to be used to initialize the graph
